uot;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;年&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;#39;Times New Roman&amp;#39;;&quot;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;月&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;#39;Times New Roman&amp;#39;;&quot;&gt;15&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;日至&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;#39;Times New Roman&amp;#39;;&quot;&gt;18&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;日，武汉隆重举办&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;#39;Times New Roman&amp;#39;;&quot;&gt;2015&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;第八届中国武汉茶业博览交易会，本次展会期间，品品香白茶健康中国行暨晒白金老白茶品鉴会（武汉站）于&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;#39;Times New Roman&amp;#39;;&quot;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;月&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;#39;Times New Roman&amp;#39;;&quot;&gt;15&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;日下午与茶友们见面。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:&amp;#39;yes&amp;#39;;font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/attached/20150515/20150515164640_3501.jpg&quot; title=&quot;品品香参加2015第八届中国武汉茶业博览交易会&quot; alt=&quot;品品香参加2015第八届中国武汉茶业博览交易会&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:&amp;#39;yes&amp;#39;;font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;品品香参加2015第八届中国武汉茶业博览交易会&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:&amp;#39;yes&amp;#39;;font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/attached/20150515/20150515164650_2253.jpg&quot; title=&quot;品品香白茶茶艺表演&quot; alt=&quot;品品香白茶茶艺表演&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:&amp;#39;yes&amp;#39;;font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;品品香白茶茶艺表演&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:&amp;#39;yes&amp;#39;;font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;品鉴会上，来自湖北陆羽茶文化研究会石爱发会长及湖北武汉等地茶友们莅临品品会现场品鉴品品香晒白金老白茶。现场，到场茶友不仅喝到了健康自然的白茶，还通过品品香邵克平总经理的讲解，了解了白茶的历史文化、品质特征、保健价值等，部分朋友更通过现场抽奖环节，赢取了品品香精心预备的大礼，同时充满意趣的猜茶环节和优雅的茶艺表演，也都赢得了茶友们的由衷喜爱。展会当天，武汉茶叶协会秘书长、华中文化书院副院长吴克喜老先生更亲临武汉会展中心品品香展馆为茶友们书法创作。&lt;img src=&quot;/attached/20150515/20150515164709_0382.jpg&quot; title=&quot;吴克喜老先生题字并与邵克平总经理合影&quot; alt=&quot;吴克喜老先生题字并与邵克平总经理合影&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:&amp;#39;yes&amp;#39;;font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt; 吴克喜老先生题字并与邵克平总经理合影&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:&amp;#39;yes&amp;#39;;font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/attached/20150515/20150515164724_4135.jpg&quot; title=&quot;获奖茶友上台领奖&quot; alt=&quot;获奖茶友上台领奖&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:&amp;#39;yes&amp;#39;;font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;获奖茶友上台领奖&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:&amp;#39;yes&amp;#39;;font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;世界白茶在中国，中国白茶在福鼎。中国白茶领导品牌品品香为弘扬白茶文化，展现白茶魅力走进武汉。品品香在政府的支持、消费者的信赖下，更加始终如一，执着于福鼎白茶文化、工艺的传承，执着于科学技术的创新、茶叶品质的突破，执着于一品再品，反复斟酌评审的茶叶标准，执着于茶叶绿色、有机、自然、健康的品质，执着于传递品品香的人文关怀和情感慰藉，执着于做大做强茶产业、兴茶惠民的远大志向。参加本届展会，除了以品鉴会吸引茶友们关注，对品品香而言，最为重要的仍是把真正自然、健康、品位的好茶在参展期间奉献给茶友们！&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;!--[if gte mso 9]&gt;&lt;xml&gt;&lt;w:latentstyles deflockedstate=&quot;false&quot; defunhidewhenused=&quot;true&quot; defsemihidden=&quot;true&quot; defqformat=&quot;false&quot; defpriority=&quot;99&quot; latentstylecount=&quot;260&quot;&gt;&lt;w:lsdexception locked=&quot;false&quot; priority=&quot;99&quot; semihidden=&quot;false&quot; name=&quot;Normal&quot;&gt;&lt;/w:lsdexception&gt;&lt;w:lsdexception locked=&quot;false&quot; priority=&quot;99&quot; semihidden=&quot;false&quot; name=&quot;heading 1&quot;&gt;&lt;/w:lsdexception&gt;&lt;w:lsdexception locked=&quot;false&quot; priority=&quot;99&quot; semihidden=&quot;false&quot; name=&quot;heading 2&quot;&gt;&lt;/w:lsdexception&gt;&lt;w:lsdexception locked=&quot;false&quot; priority=&quot;99&quot; semihidden=&quot;false&quot; name=&quot;heading 3&quot;&gt;&lt;/w:lsdexception&gt;&lt;w:lsdexception locked=&quot;false&quot; priority=&quot;99&quot; semihidden=&quot;false&quot; name=&quot;heading 4&quot;&gt;&lt;/w:lsdexception&gt;&lt;w:lsdexception locked=&quot;false&quot; priority=&quot;99&quot; semihidden=&quot;false&quot; name=&quot;heading 5&