uot;&gt;&lt;/w:lsdexception&gt;&lt;/w:latentstyles&gt;&lt;/xml&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;','/attached/20150515/20150515164640_3501.jpg'),(1946,12,'&lt;!--[if gte mso 9]&gt;&lt;xml&gt;&lt;w:worddocument&gt;&lt;w:browserlevel&gt;MicrosoftInternetExplorer4&lt;/w:browserlevel&gt;&lt;w:displayhorizontaldrawinggridevery&gt;0&lt;/w:displayhorizontaldrawinggridevery&gt;&lt;w:displayverticaldrawinggridevery&gt;2&lt;/w:displayverticaldrawinggridevery&gt;&lt;w:documentkind&gt;DocumentNotSpecified&lt;/w:documentkind&gt;&lt;w:drawinggridverticalspacing&gt;7.8 磅&lt;/w:drawinggridverticalspacing&gt;&lt;w:punctuationkerning&gt;&lt;/w:punctuationkerning&gt;&lt;w:view&gt;Normal&lt;/w:view&gt;&lt;w:compatibility&gt;&lt;w:dontgrowautofit /&gt;&lt;w:balancesinglebytedoublebytewidth /&gt;&lt;w:donotexpandshiftreturn /&gt;&lt;w:usefelayout /&gt;&lt;/w:compatibility&gt;&lt;w:zoom&gt;0&lt;/w:zoom&gt;&lt;/w:worddocument&gt;&lt;/xml&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:&amp;#39;yes&amp;#39;;font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;2015&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;年&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;#39;Times New Roman&amp;#39;;&quot;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;月&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;#39;Times New Roman&amp;#39;;&quot;&gt;15&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;日至&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;#39;Times New Roman&amp;#39;;&quot;&gt;18&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;日，品品香参展&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;#39;Times New Roman&amp;#39;;&quot;&gt;2015&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;第十二届上海国际茶业博览会。参展期间&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;#39;Times New Roman&amp;#39;;&quot;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;月&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;#39;Times New Roman&amp;#39;;&quot;&gt;16&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;日下午，品品香还举办了一场品品香白茶健康中国行暨晒白金老白茶品鉴会（上海站），上海市茶叶行业协会秘书长陈子法、上海茶叶学会秘书长周星娣、《吃茶去》杂志总编辑舒曼以及参加本次展会的各路茶友热情参与了品鉴会。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:&amp;#39;yes&amp;#39;;font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/attached/20150518/20150518142830_5379.jpg&quot; title=&quot;品品香白茶茶艺表演&quot; alt=&quot;品品香白茶茶艺表演&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:&amp;#39;yes&amp;#39;;font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt; 品品香白茶茶艺表演&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:&amp;#39;yes&amp;#39;;font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;在品鉴会现场，品品香公司总经理邵克平为茶友们解读白茶、解析品品香，并为朋友们带来了老白茶标杆品牌“晒白金”——这一具有年份、等级、产地身份的系列好茶的专业解析。现场还准备了激动人心的抽奖环节和品鉴会纪念礼品，以及别开生面的猜茶环节，以丰厚大礼回馈茶友们的热情参与。活动中，品品香白茶仙子所带来的茶艺表演，将优雅的茶艺表演与品品香白茶典雅气质进行了完美结合。&lt;img src=&quot;/attached/20150518/20150518142850_4756.jpg&quot; title=&quot;热闹的品鉴会现场&quot; alt=&quot;热闹的品鉴会现场&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:&amp;#39;yes&amp;#39;;font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt; 热闹的品鉴会现场&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:&amp;#39;yes&amp;#39;;font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/attached/20150518/20150518142902_6319.jpg&quot; title=&quot;邵克平总经理解析晒白金&quot; alt=&quot;邵克平总经理解析晒白金&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:&amp;#39;yes&amp;#39;;font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;邵克平总经理解析晒白金&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:&amp;#39;yes&amp;#39;;font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;上海是一座国际化大都市，品品香携老白茶标杆产品晒白金也已多次登上这一个广阔舞台，品品香白茶也逐步得到上海茶友们的支持和喜爱，“白茶热”已成为上海茶友圈里的常态。为让这股“白茶热”更为广泛传播，品品香再次借本次展会的召开，走进上海。除了举办本次品品香白茶健康中国行暨晒白金老白茶品鉴会（上海站），&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;#39;Times New Roman&amp;#39;;&quot;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;月&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;#39;Times New Roman&amp;#39;;&quot;&gt;15&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;日至&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:&amp;#39;Times New Roman&amp;#39;;&quot;&gt;18&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;日，品品香茶业还将在展会现场继续守候每位爱茶朋友的光临！&lt;img src=&quot;/attached/20150518/20150518142934_0696.jpg&quot; title=&quot;邵克平总经理接受媒体采访&quot; alt=&quot;邵克平总经理接受媒体采访&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:&amp;#39;yes&amp;#39;;font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;邵克平总经理接受媒体采访&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:&amp;#39;yes&amp;#39;;font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/attached/20150518/20150518142952_6010.jpg&quot; title=&quot;外国茶友前来咨询&quot; alt=&quot;外国茶友前来咨询&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;外国茶友前来咨询&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;!--[if gte mso 9]&gt;&lt;xml&gt;&lt;w:latentstyles deflockedstate=&quot;false&quot; defunhidewhenused=&quot;true&quot; defsemihidden=&quot;true&quot; defqformat=&quot;false&quot; defpriority=&quot;99&quot; latentstylecount=&quot;260&quot;&gt;&lt;w:lsdexception locked=&quot;false&quot; priority=&quot;99&quot; semihidden=&quot;false&quot; name=&quot;Normal&quot;&gt;&lt;/w:lsdexception&gt;&lt;w:lsdexception locked=&quot;false&quot; priority=&quot;99&quot; semihidden=&quot;false&quot; name=&quot;heading 1&quot;&gt;&lt;/w:lsdexception&gt;&lt;w:lsdexception locked=&quot;false&quot; priority=&quot;99&quot; semihidden=&quot;false&quot; name=&quot;heading 2&quot;&gt;&lt;/w:lsdexception&gt;&lt;w:lsdexception locked=&quot;false&quot; priority=&quot;99&quot; semihidden=&quot;false&quot; name=&quot;heading 3&quot;&gt;&lt;/w:lsdexception&gt;&lt;w:lsdexception locked=&quot;false&quot; priority=&quot;99&quot; semihidden=&quot;false&quot; name=&quot;heading 4&quot;&gt;&lt;/w:lsdexception&gt;&lt;w:lsdexception locked=&quot;false&quot; priority=&quot;99&quot; semihidden=&quot;false&quot; name=&quot;heading 5&quot;&gt;&lt;/w:lsdexception&gt;&lt;w:lsdexception locked=&quot;false&quot; priority=&quot;99&quot; semihidden=&quot;false&quot; name=&